# Crafterkite — Creative Operations OS
Premium multi-tenant SaaS (Design Pickle + Notion + HubSpot hybrid) for creative agencies.

## Stack
- Frontend: Next.js 14+ App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind, shadcn/ui, TanStack Query, Zustand
- Backend: NestJS, Prisma, PostgreSQL
- Icons: Lucide React only. IDs: CUID2.

## Design
- Dark mode default, elegant light mode support
- shadcn/ui + Tailwind only — no other component libs
- Typography: **Inter** (headings) + **Geist Mono** (code/data) — import via `next/font/google`
- Premium feel: thoughtful spacing, type hierarchy, subtle shadows, micro-interactions
- Never generic or cookie-cutter

## Rules
- `"use client"` required on any file using hooks
- No hydration errors (no mismatched server/client class or style attrs)
- Every DB query scoped to `org_id` (strict multi-tenancy)
- Keep changes minimal and focused unless told otherwise
- Code must be clean, maintainable, production-ready

## Current State
- Multi-tenancy enforced via middleware
- Auth partially set up (login bypassed)
- Sidebar: fixed 240px + DashboardHeader
- Request model: status flow + priorityOrder implemented
- Build incrementally from here

Deliver beautiful, polished, production-quality results every time.